data.description: Beautiful one owner home with 3 bedrooms, 2 full  baths and a study. Large primary bedroom with double sinks, garden tub, free standing shower and a great closet. Living room can handle large furniture and has a corner fireplace and crown moulding. The kitchen has granite countertops, microwave and dishwasher, a brand new electric stove, pull out drawers in every cabinet and pantry, and a bar eating area. The wood floors are a plus. The backyard is ready for entertaining. It has an extra large covered patio with pull down shades and ceiling fan and additional concrete. Extras include a sprinkler system and a storm shelter and gutters. Gorgeous home inside and out. You can feel the pride this homeowner has and it shows. Ready for it's new owners. Great location near Heart Hospital and close to Tinker and easy highway access. Buyer to verify all information.
